{"tid":1226893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(中國)鐵路專家 (中國)北京交大校長車禍亡","createTime":"2019-06-15T13:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T13:51:26.000Z","uid":53026,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07f289b6c27363649c2bbfc7056b663615daa813","tid":1226893,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:45:45.000Z","msg":"(中國)鐵路專家 (中國)北京交大校長車禍亡<br />\n圖1之1<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/pns/20190615/s00055/691938e2913f9372bdd7ea9fb1e14a63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F20190615%2Fs00055%2F691938e2913f9372bdd7ea9fb1e14a63.jpg&h=41b219fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】上月卸任(中國)北京交通大學校長的中國工程院院士寧濱（圖），昨在(中國)北京<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>赴「世界交通大會」途中遭遇交通🇨🇳事故🇨🇳逝世</strong></span></span>，享年60歲。寧濱對中國地鐵、火車、☭高鐵☭等軌道交通的列車運行控制系統有重要貢獻，是🇨🇳(中國)內地🇨🇳軌道交通數碼化、網絡化信號系統的開拓者和領軍者之一，曾獲鐵路行業個人最高獎「詹天佑大獎」，2016年獲「何梁何利科學與技術進步獎」。寧濱還是瑞典皇家工程科學院院士、電機暨電子工程師學會（IEEE）會士、國際鐵路信號工程師協會（IRSE）會士及中國分會主席、英國工程技術學會（IET）會士。<br />\n<br />\n（澎湃新聞）"},{"pid":"e6fe397b103f23b33a2a809ef04b513bbbd6948c","tid":1226893,"uid":93649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"被死亡"},{"pid":"49d941168d7bd1ff554589521a8fb1a051950442","tid":1226893,"uid":71237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"佢真係一生都貢獻咗比交通"},{"pid":"0b4573c623ac62aee396cae4767653587033321b","tid":1226893,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49d941168d7bd1ff554589521a8fb1a051950442","tid":1226893,"uid":71237,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:50:14.000Z","msg":"佢真係一生都貢獻咗比交通"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T13:51:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}